"keeping the spirit of GPL v2, and at the same time has been tailored to new "
"needs. ((otrs)) views GPLv3, more specifically AGPLv3, as being the best "
"balanced Copyleft Open Source License available today, offering Protection "
"for copyright owners and users and providing the best security under the "
