"linkend=\"what-is-a-queue\">queues</link> of your system (see Figure "
"below). In a new OTRS installation there are 4 default queues: Raw, Junk, "
"Misc and Postmaster. All incoming messages will be stored in the \"Raw\" "
"queue if no filter rules are defined. The \"Junk\" queue can be used to "
"store spam messages."
