#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/stats.xml:1042
msgid ""
"Prior OTRS versions 1.3 and 2.0 already facilitated the generation of stats "
"/ reports. Various reports for OTRS versions 1.3 and 2.0 which have been "
"specially developed to meet customers' requirements can be used in recent "
"OTRS versions too."
